dstat: dstat (Versatile resource statistics tool)
dstat:
dstat: Dstat is a versatile replacement for vmstat, iostat, netstat and
dstat: ifstat. Dstat overcomes some of their limitations and adds some extra
dstat: features, more counters and flexibility. Dstat is handy for monitoring
dstat: systems during performance tuning tests, benchmarks or
dstat: troubleshooting.
